description:
This is a 22 minute workout called 'Catch Compression Row' from the channel Dani Hansen.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Learn the proper catch position with Dani and practice this with three-quarter slide drills.
